Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wammy's House is not just any orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a special institute; {\alpha&HFF&}they gathered the brightest children there with the aim of raising the second L, in other words, L's successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a special institute; they gathered the brightest children there with the aim of raising the second L, in other words, L's successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all of them, a young boy named Near stood out as the top student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... is he N?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the young boy that N mentioned, Mello, was apparently the closest to Near in terms of abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near is L's successor... {\alpha&HFF&}there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near is L's successor... there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the "N" that's controlling the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}Mello must have been aiming to become L's successor as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Mello must have been aiming to become L's successor as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in which case, it's highly likely that he'll do whatever it takes to get his hands on the notebook before Near does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "Mello" that N was talking about... {\alpha&HFF&}He doesn't merely "suspect" him, there's no mistaking that he's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "Mello" that N was talking about... He doesn't merely "suspect" him, there's no mistaking that he's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are sketches of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No photos were left of either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's successor... {\alpha&HFF&}am I fighting L still?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's successor... am I fighting L still?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, the first thing I need to do is locate the mafia group that Mello's with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had Misa look through a list of currently wanted mafia members, and point him out to me using her Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found one! {\alpha&HFF&}Someone whose lifespan I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found one! Someone whose lifespan I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 105. He's listed as "Jack Neylon", but his real name is Kal Snydar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the Death Note, I manipulated Snydar into sending a sealed letter with the whereabouts of their organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should arrive soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! The letter has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in LA!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I've completely outplayed both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With both the notebook and Misa's eyes in my possession, I really am invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}Misa was able to help again, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... Misa was able to help again, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I love you, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all that remains is to test to which extent we can manipulate people with this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like them all to be able to see me and talk to me at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current owner, Snydar... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll start by getting him to touch the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current owner, Snydar... I'll start by getting him to touch the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee... {\alpha&HFF&}plonk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee... plonk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck? The notebook just jumped of its own accord...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a notebook that can kill people. It'd hardly be surprising if it turned out to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}Boss!! The guy in the weird, dirty costume... is he a new recruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!! {\alpha&HFF&}The guy in the weird, dirty costume... is he a new recruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!! The guy in the weird, dirty costume... {\alpha&HFF&}is he a new recruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!! The guy in the weird, dirty costume... is he a new recruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a recruit, I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to be visible to the others, just have them touch the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Apparently, if you touch the notebook you'll be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Apparently, if you touch the notebook you'll be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I need you to touch the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going crazy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, try touching the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw anything the last time I touched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Should we kill it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. Humans can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this Shinigami really exists, and is telling the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, {\alpha&HFF&}as of now, I'm relinquishing ownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, as of now, I'm relinquishing ownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to accompany whoever becomes the next owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! You're giving up your ownership?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do that, won't you lose your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I do this, even if I relinquish the ownership of my notebook, I won't lose my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut out pages when you need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you'll have to play the part of Kira. Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... but what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to make any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "chocolate" stuff is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what you just said, is it really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the person using the note fails to continously write names of people to be killed within 13 days of each other, then the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "If you make this note unusable by tearing it up or burning it, all the humans who have touched the note till then will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these two rules really fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're completely false.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami probably wrote that as a joke before giving it to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can check whether the "13 days" rule is true or not by having someone test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem here is whether or not Kira has used this notebook before, {\alpha&HFF&}and if they have, whether they know these rules are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem here is whether or not Kira has used this notebook before, and if they have, {\alpha&HFF&}whether they know these rules are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem here is whether or not Kira has used this notebook before, and if they have, whether they know these rules are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do know, {\alpha&HFF&}then they could use these rules... especially this "13 days" rule... it could be used to prove someones innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do know, then they could use these rules... {\alpha&HFF&}especially this "13 days" rule... it could be used to prove someones innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do know, then they could use these rules... especially this "13 days" rule... {\alpha&HFF&}it could be used to prove someones innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do know, then they could use these rules... especially this "13 days" rule... it could be used to prove someones innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sidoh! {\alpha&HFF&}Keep watch outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sidoh! Keep watch outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be useful, as humans won't be able to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep watch outside. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy? {\alpha&HFF&}For a human, he sure is... scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy? For a human, he sure is... {\alpha&HFF&}scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy? For a human, he sure is... scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook that was in the hands of the Japanese investigation has been stolen by criminals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira? {\alpha&HFF&}If you're really Kira, prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira? If you're really Kira, prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof? {\alpha&HFF&}Now that the notebook has fallen into other hands, committing an announced murder will no longer prove that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof? Now that the notebook has fallen into other hands, {\alpha&HFF&}committing an announced murder will no longer prove that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof? Now that the notebook has fallen into other hands, committing an announced murder will no longer prove that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you should shortly receive proof that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the notebook I'm giving you, you'll be able to see a person's name merely by looking at them. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li-{\alpha&HFF&}st-en care-fully...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li-st-{\alpha&HFF&}en care-fully...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li-st-en {\alpha&HFF&}care-fully...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li-st-en care-{\alpha&HFF&}fully...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li-st-en care-fully...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On November 10th at 23:59,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:10:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all mafia members that I've been able to identify from information taken from the FBI and other organizations will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has already been written in the notebook, and cannot be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know the location of their hideout, and I'll pass that along with the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, {\alpha&HFF&}that moment, the 10th of November at 23:59, will be your greatest chance to retrieve your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that moment, {\alpha&HFF&}the 10th of November at 23:59, will be your greatest chance to retrieve your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that moment, the 10th of November at 23:59, {\alpha&HFF&}will be your greatest chance to retrieve your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that moment, the 10th of November at 23:59, will be your greatest chance to retrieve your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the mafia die on day X as Kira said, {\alpha&HFF&}it would definitely be a big chance for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the mafia die on day X as Kira said, it would definitely be a big chance for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm uncomfortable with following Kira's plan, but it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, all we actually know is when the mafia will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide-san, you say that, but you must already have realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're being asked to do the deal for the eyes of a Shinigami and ensure we kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-{\alpha&HFF&}No way! If anyone's going to do the deal, it should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! {\alpha&HFF&}If anyone's going to do the deal, it should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! If anyone's going to do the deal, it should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who handed the notebook over in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I've even thought about ending my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the notebook to kill those criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}and then after 13 days, I'll die myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the notebook to kill those criminals, and then after 13 days, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll die myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the notebook to kill those criminals, and then after 13 days, I'll die myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If father ends up writing the names in the notebook, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:51.31,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,388)\fad(500,0)}10th November 23:47
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, are you all prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. {\alpha&HFF&}Deputy Chief Yagami, go ahead and exchange your eyes with the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Deputy Chief Yagami, {\alpha&HFF&}go ahead and exchange your eyes with the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Deputy Chief Yagami, go ahead and exchange your eyes with the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief Yagami, {\alpha&HFF&}can you see the names and lifespans of the criminals in the photos I passed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief Yagami, can you see the names and lifespans of the criminals in the photos I passed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When those names disappear, that's your signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Kira has gotten involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've already gotten this far... {\alpha&HFF&}we haven't perfected our plans yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've already gotten this far... we haven't perfected our plans yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}Sidoh, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Sidoh, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and watch, Sidoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't meddle in this, you'll get your notebook back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roy! Skiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook is under Rodd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it up to the monitor room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, two of the mafia members have been captured and the notebook safely retrieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}it's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't found anyone that fits the description of Mello yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely hiding somewhere in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already made it this far. We'll need to search for him slowly and calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move. {\alpha&HFF&}I've sealed off both exits with that one blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move. I've sealed off both exits with that one blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was merely a threat... {\alpha&HFF&}next, I'll blow the whole hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was merely a threat... next, I'll blow the whole hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow my orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's you again, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have killed you the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined I would be doing a deal for the notebook with you a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}I-H-A-E-L K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-{\alpha&HFF&}H-A-E-L K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-{\alpha&HFF&}A-E-L K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-{\alpha&HFF&}E-L K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-{\alpha&HFF&}L K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-L {\alpha&HFF&}K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-L K-{\alpha&HFF&}E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-L K-E-{\alpha&HFF&}E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-L K-E-E-{\alpha&HFF&}H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-L K-E-E-H-{\alpha&HFF&}L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-I-H-A-E-L K-E-E-H-L
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your real name is Mihael Keehl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Mello. {\alpha&HFF&}If you come along quietly, we won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Mello. If you come along quietly, {\alpha&HFF&}we won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Mello. If you come along quietly, we won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Why are you saying such idiotic things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you saying such idiotic things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just write his name in the notebook and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I write your name in this notebook, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move your hands away from the switch and raise them in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! {\alpha&HFF&}All I need to write now is your family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! All I need to write now is your family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take less than a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! {\alpha&HFF&}Just write it! Write it down now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Just write it! {\alpha&HFF&}Write it down now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Just write it! Write it down now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I honestly never had any intention of killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... {\alpha&HFF&}I bet you've never killed anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... I bet you've never killed anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunshots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jose! The notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Let go... of the notebook!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! Put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you look alright to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L! There's no sign of Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said to kill him sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? {\alpha&HFF&}Father?! I'm begging you! Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? Father?! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm begging you! Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? Father?! I'm begging you! {\alpha&HFF&}Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? Father?! I'm begging you! Please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're glad? {\alpha&HFF&}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're glad? Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still... {\alpha&HFF&}have the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still... have the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuk, I can't see the lifespan of anyone who owns a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Shinigami, Ryuk, {\alpha&HFF&}I can't see the lifespan of anyone who owns a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Shinigami, Ryuk, I can't see the lifespan of anyone who owns a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}you aren't Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... you aren't Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he's not. I can't believe you're still saying things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, don't speak more than necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's important too, {\alpha&HFF&}but right now, there's something even more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's important too, but right now, there's something even more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like writing Mello's name into the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I'm sorry... in the end, I couldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry... {\alpha&HFF&}in the end, I couldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry... in the end, {\alpha&HFF&}I couldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry... in the end, I couldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be strange if I say "It's not too late" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I guess it'll depend on how I phrase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, it's not unnatural to be confused and upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! {\alpha&HFF&}Use the last of your strength and write that bastards name down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Use the last of your strength and write that bastards name down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to go down beaten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die! You fool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Shinigami who came to retrieve this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's for the sake of the Kira investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}we only need one notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's for the sake of the Kira investigation, we only need one notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning this one.
